{"tid":294204,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"講下你地初戀係點","createTime":"2017-06-22T18:02:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T13:38:30.000Z","uid":54581,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"959bb8f3008b82dbe96560dacf14bf8fb407e9cd","tid":294204,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T18:02:04.000Z","msg":"個時中學雞 同個女仔係msn chat 左成年咁濟 個陣一online就震佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同佢玩小遊戲<br />\n<br />\n我記得係表左幾次白先成功，第一次on99 係張白紙寫地啲示愛說話，叫佢圈Yes / No<br />\n佢圈晒兩樣，叫我俾時間佢諗下<br />\n<br />\n最後係親口表白成功<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個時初初勁單純，完全無諗過扑野個啲野<br />\n最多好似啲電視劇咁，攬下佢 拖住手放學搭地鐵<br />\n<br />\n我記得係拍左兩個禮拜拖先至錫佢第一啖，好似係校運會黎 吹住海風啜佢一啖<br />\n<br />\n最後有做啲sweet野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但都係完全無諗過做愛個啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家諗起好後悔，唔係我就可以破學生妹處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （散個陣佢已夠稱）"},{"pid":"4abcc5dd3afb3e918b5d9ea11a6988ce24172c4a","tid":294204,"uid":42734,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T18:02:55.000Z","msg":"我都想知係點"},{"pid":"f809f61bfb46b7c2ae66a24bfe92948a2ee3edd6","tid":294204,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T18:05:40.000Z","msg":"今日又唔想9up<br />\n<br />\n想傾下開心野<br />\n<br />\n諗起都幾開心其實<br />\n<br />\n依家識女我都會帶佢行我以前番學會經過既地方 懷緬下"},{"pid":"69c721a4824947355ddadae98b428251fbc6989a","tid":294204,"uid":78683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T18:06:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想知係點</blockquote><br />\n我愛你 我地一齊捽碟"},{"pid":"f4b87ed64b703077997f5eecb5215cc3a973f9e3","tid":294204,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T18:07:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都想知係點</blockquote><br />\n我愛你 我地一齊捽碟</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936aab900f831fdd7b6924e847d40959f3efeb8c","tid